fuzzel|1.11.0|Wayland-native application launcher|x86_64|MIT|wayland, pixman, fcft, freetype, fontconfig
neofetch|7.1.0|System information tool written in bash|x86_64|MIT|
micro|2.0.14|Modern terminal text editor (single Go binary)|x86_64|MIT|
steam|1.0.0.79|Steam digital distribution platform|x86_64|custom:Proprietary|glibc, libcurl, dbus, libx11
nano|8.2|Small friendly terminal text editor|x86_64|GPL-3.0|ncurses
htop|3.3.0|Interactive process viewer|x86_64|GPL-2.0|ncurses
example|1.0.0|Template for creating CDOSUP packages|x86_64|MIT|
